Class HeapPriorityQueue<AnyKey extends java.lang.Comparable<? super AnyKey>,AnyValue extends java.lang.Comparable<? super AnyValue>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • correlator.HeapPriorityQueue<AnyKey,AnyValue>
  • Type Parameters:
    AnyKey - the key.
    AnyValue - the value.

    public class HeapPriorityQueue<AnyKey extends java.lang.Comparable<? super AnyKey>,AnyValue extends java.lang.Comparable<? super AnyValue>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements a priority queue of comparable objects using a max-heap represented as an array. Line#51 was changed to use a greater-than operator to make this a max-heap.
    Version:
    5.27C
    Author:
    BJP, Monika, modified by Sam Brendel
